its and release them in the map!\nThe left and right sticks allow you to move the user's position slightly.\n\n[Type of Units]\n-Base\nThis is the Base.\nBuild your Base stronger!!\n\n-Fighter\nA common flying unit.\nGround & Air Attack.\n\n-Factory\nA factory unit.\nIt generates cash.\n\n-Bomber\nA flying unit skilled for\nbombing and ground attack.\n\n-Tank\nAn anti-ground unit.\nAttacks with rapid fire.\n\n-Anti-aircraft Artillery\nA placement unit using missles.\nEffective to flying units.\n\n-Sheild\nA placement unit for defense.\nIt has high durability.\n", "short_description": "Let's play a VR video game with your girl friend!\nThis time it's a strategy game.\nPick up the units and release them in the map.\nThe units will start fighting automatically."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "PdpArt_3000x900_JP.png", "id": "266102791924715", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974650_266102795258048_1135847423250422851_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8MDXQ_B49dEQ7kNvgGsCOLq&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AKcXmXP_i5W3YZqeX7d0gg2&oh=00_AYDvTB_QZ_QfT8Cee8JxPFqhOlM3yFRx49GoP3DELxTGew&oe=66E41DB4"}, {"file_name": "Art_1008x1440.png", "id": "4244000545622202", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974522_4244000548955535_6121386002098751284_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=b0hrKMNb4PUQ7kNvgFdemgY&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AKcXmXP_i5W3YZqeX7d0gg2&oh=00_AYAGlIIZMDd8Y_I5FCv9GMu55he19w9fRMU67qmoXlyfTg&oe=66E43E45"}, {"file_name": "Art_2560x1440.png", "id": "3609745079249612", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974800_3609745082582945_8822499596742085698_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7Xii5CSfQIcQ7kNvgEDsKtT&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AKcXmXP_i5W3YZqeX7d0gg2&oh=00_AYCKR_SXp8Q9_FE_k72rgZ1jAhERWXYYefHygpWDSrwFKg&oe=66E4360C"}, {"f